  "description": {
    "canonical": "Matter from the body of the Wyrm Fass, purged of toxins, and rendered usefully. Used to attract Aquapulmo and Flagellocanth in Cambion Drift surface hotspots, Aquapulmo only during Vome.\n\nObtained from Daughter in the Necralisk (Deimos).",
    "display": "来自于蛟龙“混乱”身上的物质，清除了毒素后变得有用了。可以用来吸引魔胎之境地面鱼点中的水肺和须腔棘鱼、“秩序”期间的水肺。\n\n从殁世幽都（火卫二）的“女儿”处获得。"
  },
